    "description": "<strong>STACK STONES</strong>, a physics based multiplayer stacking and party game. Enjoy playing alone to beat your former best mark or compete against others in funny multiplayer matches ... but watch out for your opponents, they want to smash your stack!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/04df497e993ed9fc64aa248e98b20799.webp?t=1689774107\" width=400 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/1cee41a3b184a6b6d53c9571351c9522.poster.avif?t=1689774107\" width=412 height=172 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/1cee41a3b184a6b6d53c9571351c9522.webm?t=1689774107\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/1cee41a3b184a6b6d53c9571351c9522.mp4?t=1689774107\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build your stack and reach the height target as fast and with as less stones as you can.<br>The higher you go, the less stable your stack will get, so be careful!<br>Enjoy all if this in different <strong>game modes</strong> like ...<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>... Stack Race<br></li><li>... Last Stack Standing<br></li><li>... Puzzle Speed Stacking<br></li><li>... Stone Rain</li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/6a73806c8b84f7645aa96d9af561b67a.webp?t=1689774107\" width=317 height=42 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199820/extras/913d2d421994c845c4e78fdeeb3ac7b7.poster.avif?t=1689774107\" width=412 